casebody.data:
No. 73,

Misc.

Clewis v. Texas. Reagan H. Legg for petitioner. Waggoner Carr, Attorney General of Texas, Hawthorne Phillips, First Assistant Attorney General, and Howard M. Fender, Assistant Attorney General, for respondent.

Ct. Crim. App. Tex. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari granted. Case transferred to appellate docket.
